account.descriptionLink:
This is the first of several proposals to test the engagement of the community in the OKU DAO for the purposes of Benchmarking our MAXIMUM ENGAGEMENT THRESHOLD. 

We need everyone to vote for this proposal to help us accurately set up the new Xandeum DAO. There will be no programmed instructions associated with this proposal, it will only serve as a history we can use in setting up the new DAO.

The overall time for voting is set to 4.5 days. The first 4 days will be for unrestricted voting, and the last 12 hours of cool-down can only be used to vote NO for a proposal.
account.name: Adopt New Brand Name "XANDEUM"
